        "story": {
            "title": "Our Story",
            "description": "Founded in 2020, our journey is built on over 20 years of passion for sports, starting at the age of 17 and growing through kabaddi, strength & conditioning, CrossFit, powerlifting, and bodybuilding. At 37, one Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu class after lockdown changed everything — the passion turned into a mission. Since then, we’ve been training in BJJ for the past two years and have successfully conducted four exciting MMA events to build our community. Our goal is simple: to help people of all ages learn MMA, discover their strength, and unlock their true potential. MMA is not just about looking fit — it’s about feeling powerful, confident, and ready to conquer every challenge life throws at you.",
            "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAavW2vwX_Nu-gJ5R-esTpR8zGseWcv2FBajqZnvOcW-EuGpD8_QzOozZYiwzE05E3nutPGd61vhIqNzcbaBfnIfu7DjI9JfEwyMQv6YBOJdgkrlpHyEI2cjtAX3TTpWgxE7-diivtpdjeclZ8oxWr9Q9RpRuaKL2-_Voc4GdgRMMvzKMKdzgkJtyYIi3SXmhEb-QqYjHhQibf-8pD8b9oflnHHJpxOpDjUKv_deysKP2RC1uqx8C_SnKAGMCXZE3zgxI_IjN1zAF0"
